Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.62,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(640,600)}「花坂结衣定下约定」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么样都理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真擅长教人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很合适做老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…关于这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话 以后也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始也请你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还用得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 突然登门造访
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就没水了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停水…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澡堂吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢陪我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…洗好之后能稍微等一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去也想一起什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜风真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在想东京究竟是怎样的地方 我能好好过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉我也能拼一拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各方面都要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体要变凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.11,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}目の前の扉を開けたら春風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.53,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}鳥たちも樹木で待ち合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:42.28,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}君へ向かう信号は青空色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.45,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}駆けだせばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.49,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}嘘つき確率論とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.04,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}1+1=∞とか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:56.00,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}教えてくれた君と探しに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.63,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}春待ちクローバー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.11,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}打开面前的门迎来春风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}鸟儿们在树上等候着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:42.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}通往你的信号显示着天蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}笔直向前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.49,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}说谎机率论啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.04,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}1+1=∞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:56.00,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\blur3\fad(150,150)}与将这些告诉我的你一起去寻找
